  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to provide the information of tissue elasticity in different etiologies of&#xD;
      pleural lesions and to validate the predictive value of shear-wave elastography in&#xD;
      differentiating benign pleural lesions from malignant lesions.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
